Title: Urticaria successfully treated by desensitization with grass pollen extract.
Abstract: We report a case of severe incapacitating seasonal urticaria and angioedema in an 11-year-old boy due to grass pollen sensitivity, who responded well to desensitization therapy with Timothy grass pollen extract.
