Title: A review of 102 cases of hypospadias treated by the Van der Meulen procedure.
Abstract: One hundred and two cases of hypospadias without chordee which were corrected by van der Meulen's operation were reviewed. There were no fistulas and only 10 complications. The functional result was good in 90 per cent.
